data.description: You'll feel "at home" as soon as you come in! This adorable home boasts 4 bedrooms and is in great condition! Situated on over 2 acres, this home has new exterior paint, brand new windows installed just weeks ago, brand new rain gutters, new garage door & front door, a new pellet stove & so much more! When you enter the home, you have a great sized living room that leads to an eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances. The upper level has 3 bedrooms + a full bathroom and the lower level has a family room with a walk-out basement and the primary bedroom + another full bathroom. The backyard is a blank slate whether you're looking for room for horses, kids or pets and plenty of room to park the toys as well!
